{
  "page": "Sworn shield",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the novella, see <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dany_Jorah_Kneeling.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/52/Dany_Jorah_Kneeling.jpg/350px-Dany_Jorah_Kneeling.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"263\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/52/Dany_Jorah_Kneeling.jpg/525px-Dany_Jorah_Kneeling.jpg 1.5x, /images/5/52/Dany_Jorah_Kneeling.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dany_Jorah_Kneeling.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> pledges to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, by Amok © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>A <b>sworn shield</b> or <b>sworn sword</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> or similar warrior who makes an oath to serve an individual<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> often as a bodyguard,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> soldier,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> or champion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Duties\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Duties</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Known_sworn_shields_and_swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known sworn shields and swords</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Historical\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Historical</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Duties\">Duties</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sworn_shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Duties\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Many <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> and lordlings keep a retinue of <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> and sworn swords in their service, including at court.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> Sworn swords can fight in their lord's host during wartime.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> are a specialized and most prestigious type of sworn shield, sworn to the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Andals,_the_Rhoynar,_and_the_First_Men\" title=\"King of the Andals, the Rhoynar, and the First Men\">King of the Andals, the Rhoynar, and the First Men</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> However, an individual Kingsguard may be appointed the sworn shield of another member of the royal family,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_viserys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_viserys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> and a non-Kingsguard may also serve as the king's sworn shield.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sworn_shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Harwin_Strong_by_Laura_Avellino.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ef/Harwin_Strong_by_Laura_Avellino.jpg/350px-Harwin_Strong_by_Laura_Avellino.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ef/Harwin_Strong_by_Laura_Avellino.jpg/525px-Harwin_Strong_by_Laura_Avellino.jpg 1.5x, /images/e/ef/Harwin_Strong_by_Laura_Avellino.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Harwin_Strong_by_Laura_Avellino.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harwin_Strong\" title=\"Harwin Strong\">Harwin Strong</a>, by Laura Avellino ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Bennis_of_the_Brown_Shield\" title=\"Bennis of the Brown Shield\">Bennis of the Brown Shield</a> were <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knights</a> who swore their service to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_Osgrey\" title=\"Eustace Osgrey\">Eustace Osgrey</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knight</a>'s quarrel with Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_sworn_shields_and_swords\">Known sworn shields and swords</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sworn_shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known sworn shields and swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical\">Historical</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sworn_shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Historical\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Tyrell\" title=\"Alester Tyrell\">Alester Tyrell</a>, for King <a href=\"/index.php/Gwayne_V_Gardener\" title=\"Gwayne V Gardener\">Gwayne V Gardener</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Orys_Baratheon\" title=\"Orys Baratheon\">Orys Baratheon</a>, for Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_house_baratheon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_house_baratheon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gyles_Morrigen\" title=\"Gyles Morrigen\">Gyles Morrigen</a>, for King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jonquil_Darke\" title=\"Jonquil Darke\">Jonquil Darke</a>, for Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a>, for Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup> later Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alicent_Hightower\" title=\"Alicent Hightower\">Alicent Hightower</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harwin_Strong\" title=\"Harwin Strong\">Harwin Strong</a>, for Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> (replacing Criston)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Erryk_Cargyll\" title=\"Erryk Cargyll\">Erryk Cargyll</a>, for Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> (replacing Harwin)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Thorne\" title=\"Rickard Thorne\">Rickard Thorne</a>, for Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maelor_Targaryen\" title=\"Maelor Targaryen\">Maelor Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Florian_Greysteel\" title=\"Florian Greysteel\">Florian Greysteel</a>, for Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfryd_Mooton\" title=\"Manfryd Mooton\">Manfryd Mooton</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Willis_Fell\" title=\"Willis Fell\">Willis Fell</a>, for Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaera_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaera Targaryen\">Jaehaera Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a>, for Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rthk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-17\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\"><i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sworn_shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Song of Ice and Fire\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/23/J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg/350px-J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/23/J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg/525px-J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/23/J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg/700px-J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:J._Edwin_StevensBodyguard.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> protecting <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Jo